quran[11{c,v,t}:
2,6,jo log kafir hain inhen tum nasiyaat karo ya nah karo un ke liye barabar hai. woh imaan nahi laane ke
2,7,khuda ne un ke dilon aur kaanon par mohar laga rakhi hai aur un ki aankhon par parda ( para howa ) hai aur un ke liye bara azaab ( tayyar ) hai
2,8,aur baaz log aisay hain jo kehte hain ke hum khuda par aur rozِ akhirat par imaan rakhtay hain halaank woh imaan nahi rakhtay
2,9,yeh ( apne Pindar mein ) khuda ko aur mominoun ko chakma dete hain magar ( haqeeqat mein ) apne siwa kisi ko chakma nahi dete aur is se be khabar hain
2,10,un ke dilon mein ( kufar ka ) marz tha. khuda ne un ka marz aur ziyada kar diya aur un ke jhoot bolnay ke sabab un ko dukh dainay wala azaab hoga
2,11,"aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke zameen mein fasaad nah daalo to kehte hain, hum to islaah karne walay hain"
2,12,"dekho yeh bilashuba mufsid hain, lekin khabar nahi rakhtay"
2,13,"aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke jis terhan aur log imaan le aeye, tum bhi imaan le aao to kehte hain, bhala jis terhan be waqoof imaan le aeye hain isi terhan hum bhi imaan le ayen? sun lau ke yahi be waqoof hain lekin nahi jantay"
2,14,"aur yeh log jab mominoun se mlitay hain to kehte hain ke hum imaan le aeye hain, aur jab apne shaitano mein jatay hain to ( un se ) kehte hain ke hum tumhare sath hain aur ( perwan Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam se ) to hum hansikiya karte hain"
2,15,un ( mnafqon ) se khuda hansi karta hai aur inhen mohlat diye jata hai ke shararat wa sarkashi mein parre behak rahay hain
2,16,"yeh woh log hain jinhon ne hadaayat chore kar gumraahi khareedi, to nah to un ki tijarat hi ne kuch naffa diya aur nah woh hadaayat yab hi hue"
